---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Vape Hire — £5 per session · Mary Jane's Place"
  description="Hire a clean, serviced dry-herb vaporiser at Mary Jane's Place for £5 per session. Walk in, ask at the counter, use a real medical-grade device — no subscription, no commitment."
>
  <section class="ph-top pad">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">Vape hire</div>
      <h1 class="rv">A clean vaporiser. £5. While you're here.</h1>
      <p class="rv lede" style="margin-top:16px">
        Don't own a vaporiser yet? Forgot yours at home? Want to try a different model
        before you spend £200+? Use one of ours during your visit — no booking, no
        subscription, no commitment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="rent-single rv">
        <div class="rent-headline">
          <div class="rent-tier">Session hire</div>
          <div class="rent-price"><b>£5</b><span>per session</span></div>
          <p style="margin-top:6px">Walk in, ask at the counter, and we'll set you up with a fully cleaned device.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="checks rent-feats">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg><span><b>A range of patient-tested devices</b> — Mighty+, Crafty+, Tinymight, Arizer and more</span></li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg><span><b>Fully sanitised between users</b> — fresh screens, mouthpiece and chamber</span></li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg><span><b>Help on hand</b> — staff can walk you through temperature, packing and technique</span></li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg><span><b>Try before you buy</b> — session fee credited if you go on to purchase the same device</span></li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn" href="/visit#contact" style="margin-top:8px">Plan a visit <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap two vc">
      <div class="rv">
        <div class="eyebrow kick">How it works</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:11px">No app. No booking. Just ask.</h2>
        <p>
          Vape hire is a counter service. You arrive, get verified as a patient (once),
          ask for the device you'd like to try, and we set you up. Each device is cleaned
          and re-sanitised between users, so what you get is always fresh.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">
          If you're not sure which one to try, tell us about your prescription and how you
          medicate — we'll suggest a couple to start with.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv card">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:10px">Want to own one?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15.5px">
          Every device you can hire here is also for sale in our
          <a class="tlink" href="/shop">shop</a>. Spend a few sessions trying different models,
          then buy the one that works for you — and we'll credit what you've already spent on
          hire toward the purchase price of the same device.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="disc rv">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 8v5M12 16h.01"/></svg>
        <div>
          Hire is available to verified medical cannabis patients with a valid prescription. We do not supply
          cannabis — patients bring their own lawfully prescribed medicine.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .rent-single {
    background: var(--olive-d);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 38px 42px;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px -28px rgba(16, 59, 20, 0.6);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 38px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .rent-headline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .rent-single .rent-tier {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--sage-soft);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .rent-single .rent-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; }
  .rent-single .rent-price b {
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .rent-single .rent-price span { font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }
  .rent-single p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); font-size: 15.5px; }
  .rent-feats li { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .rent-feats li b { color: #fff; }
  .rent-feats li svg { color: var(--sage-soft); }
  .rent-single .btn {
    align-self: start;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--olive-d);
    border-color: #fff;
  }
  .rent-single .btn:hover { background: var(--cream); border-color: var(--cream); }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .rent-single { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 28px 24px; gap: 22px; }
    .rent-single .rent-price b { font-size: 52px; }
  }
</style>
